Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:09.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:12.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:16.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:24.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:34.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:41.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:48.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:56.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:59.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:03.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:07.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:10.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:14.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:21.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:25.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:29.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:32.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:35.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:41.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:49.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.52,0:01:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was shot twice from the front,\Nand thrice from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened in that\Nroom last night, but it sure was brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An extra edition! Extra! Extra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell did it?! I'm not\Ngonna let him get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you, Straw Hat Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did this as retaliation for my\Nstealing your 200 million Berries?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, don't be shy, ask me my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:41.56,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Gum-Gum Human vs. Fire-breathing Cyborg"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be here, Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? That perv called my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't people call him Franky just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the one who beat up Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This money is already ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it... back to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Bikini guy!\N--Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no information available?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.77,0:04:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalifa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enter the room... quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...? Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san has...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's excellent news!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I'm glad you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please focus on resting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take care of the stuff at the shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, about the culprits that\Nbroke into my room last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... they're still investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:05:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were two. One was\Na big man with a mask on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a tall woman with long, black hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mistake about it.\NThose black eyes belong to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:28.34,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"He regained consciousness"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.40,0:05:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san regained consciousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is that true?!\N--All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Good!\N--All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are... Straw Hat Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:06:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went on quite the rampage\Nwhile I was gone, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I got back, I couldn't believe my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.39,0:06:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my house is totally unrecognizable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you also treat\Nmy underlings so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop me this week!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you say,\Nuntil I tear you up like rags,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my anger won't subside!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, you!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.42,0:06:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do with our money?!\NThe 200 million Berries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.30,0:06:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! 200 million Berries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already spent it! It's completely gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get all uppity and try to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the money you stole from\Nsomewhere! You're just pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It doesn't matter.\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.19,0:06:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not true! Money does matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:07:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I won't be\Nhappy until I beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me who won't be happy, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come down here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This is it! Franky is\Ngonna start going on a rampage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evacuate! Everyone, evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.71,0:07:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shot fire out of his mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never seen anyone who\Nshoots fire out of their mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he might have Devil Fruit powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him? He jumped into the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he an idiot? If he ate a\NDevil Fruit, he'll drown and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he slipped and fell.\NHe must have fire-breathing powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! He can swim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't eat any Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:10:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...? You guys didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a modified human... A cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Straw Hats, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. My own investigation\Nled to the same culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had Lucci confirm it\Nwith the government. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coo coo! Yeah... When I\Ncontacted the government,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they said that she's one\Nof the Straw Hats. Coo coo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... they, the Straw Hats, are the culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:11:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! Did they do it to get back\Nat us since we wouldn't fix their ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter the reason,\Nthe truth is that they did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can ask them the reason\Nafter we tie them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you have to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll pay for this, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes peeled for\NRobin-chan, Chopper. Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hm?\N--Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna must be pretty crazy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They say that the town gets submerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be someone who doesn't\Nknow such a storm surge is coming, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:11:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, his ship might\Nget damaged quite a bit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Say, Sanji--\N--Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you said you\Nforgot something at the Merry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... we can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, whatever it is I left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:13:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too loud, Tilestone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! You all be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Iceberg-san! I'm really\Nglad that you came around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You speak each and every word too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't good for him, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You're right! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! There's trouble!\NListen, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come inside the room.\NSpeak from where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At Dock #1, the pirate Straw Hat,\Nwho came yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,started a fight with Franky\Nand they're wrecking the shipyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...! How dare he just\Nshow up at the Dock like that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get some rest, Iceberg-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be here by your side, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out! It's coming down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship is breaking down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! This fight is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Beat up that bikini bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm gonna... beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead if you can!\NYour attacks don't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you pull all this crap?\NWhat's your goal, Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galley-La... What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the foremen from Dock #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! The foremen are finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close! The shipyard\Nalmost got destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.81,0:16:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! They're the shipwrights\Nwe met yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're on our side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, guys from Galley-La!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't butt into our fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.41,0:16:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you messed up our factory this much,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't even need a reason to come stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Franky! How are\Nyou gonna settle this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec, Tilestone.\NWe'll talk about it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have more important business right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Straw Hat Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I'm talking about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.43,0:17:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised that you\Ncould show your face again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why? We came here because\Nwe heard the news about pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Our family wasn't enough,\Nso you messed with Galley-La, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys all going through puberty,\Nhurting everyone you come across?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, we didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you play innocent, then we'll\Njust put the screws on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rope Action Half Knot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe... I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Air... Drive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastards! I said don't\Ninterfere! Don't you get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:18:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who holds the grudge against him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coo coo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat them up, Galley-La Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The company's strongest five are fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? Why are the\Nshipwrights fighting against us, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.29,0:18:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itching, itching...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait! I don't have the\Nslightest reason to fight you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's... got Devil Fruit powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you bastards, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's my prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to play with you, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say, you wild monkey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's interfering here is you, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Tilestone!\NHe's super strong, as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coo coo! Coo coo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk...! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are really strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What's with you guys?!\NTell me the reason at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat... We're the ones\Nwho'd like to know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprits who broke in to our main office\Nlast night and attacked Iceberg-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...were from your gang, weren't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be... This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They butted into my fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was... without a doubt, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that big guy next to her\Nalso one of the Straw Hats?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did they attack me in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to think that they\Ndid it as payback for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must really be after one of my possessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, are those pirates\Nconnected to the government?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are they after "that" on their own?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,News flash! News flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.56,0:21:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From what Iceberg-san said,\Nthe culprits have been identified!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's let the entire town know\Nimmediately and corner the culprits!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them leave Water Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture the culprits!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprits who attacked Mr. Iceberg are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Straw Hat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:09.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:29.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:32.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:34.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.01,0:22:37.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:40.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:52.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:55.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:57.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:00.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:08.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! How dare you hurt Iceberg-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, we didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.80,0:23:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this,\Nwe just have to ask pops in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I won't let you go!\N--Hold it! What about our fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.64,0:23:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere, Franky! I guess I've got\Nno choice. I'll just beat you both up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.69,0:23:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Straw Hat Pirates Are the Culprits?\NThe Protectors of the City of Water"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
